fields.descriptive_line:
'The Nell Gwyn Portfolio, a Series of Portraits Illustrating Her Life', by Edwin Roffe, R. B. Parkes, R. Josey and Edward Stodart et al.
[prints] Cover for 'The Nell Gwyn Portfolio, a Series of Portraits Illustrating Her Life', by  Edwin Roffe, R. B. Parkes, R. Josey and Edward Stodart et al.
[prints] Title page for 'The Nell Gwyn Portfolio, a Series of Portraits Illustrating Her Life', by Edwin Roffe, R. B. Parkes, R. Josey and Edward Stodart et al. The page features head and shoulder potraits of Nell Gwyn's two sons, James Lord Beauclerk and Charles Beauclerk, the Duke of St. Albans.
